text: Roman Lutoškin (born 11 May 1964) is an Estonian rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Estonian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Estonia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pärnu
